---
import Container from "../../../layouts/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "./Paragraph.astro";
import StarIcon from "./StarIcon.astro";
---


<Container
  className=" 4xl:grid-cols-[1fr,auto] 4xl:gap-32 4xl:pt-28 grid cursor-default grid-cols-1 bg-gradient-to-t from-[--color-secondary-lighter] pb-12 pt-20"
>
  <div class="z-10 col-span-full row-span-full sm:mr-[20vw] lg:mr-[30vw]">
    <h2
      class="pb-3 text-2xl font-semibold capitalize leading-tight tracking-normal"
    >
      Meet Our Team
    </h2>

    <Paragraph>
      We are a dedicated team led by Ruslan, a seasoned real estate agent with a
      passion for helping clients find their ideal properties. With over a decade of
      experience and numerous successful transactions, Ruslan brings a wealth of
      expertise to every client interaction, ensuring a seamless and rewarding real
      estate journey.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
      Integrity and trust are the cornerstones of our work. Ruslan has a client
      satisfaction rate of 95%, with a proven track record in residential and commercial
      property sales. Our commitment is to make each transaction as stress-free as
      possible, and we take pride in the strong relationships we've built with our
      clients.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
      Join us in exploring your next investment or dream home. For us, real estate is
      more than a transactionâ€”it's a meaningful adventure that brings real value to
      our clients. We invite you to experience the personalized service and dedication
      that sets Ruslan apart in the industry.
    </Paragraph>
  </div>

  <StarIcon
    className="col-span-full row-span-full h-[28vw] max-h-[18rem] min-h-[15rem] w-[28vw] min-w-[15rem] max-w-[18rem] translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/4 place-self-end text-[--color-secondary] opacity-20 sm:translate-y-[10%] sm:opacity-50 xl:-translate-x-0"
  />
</Container>